		<description><![CDATA[<p>As writers, we want to make our characters as unique and interesting as possible. One way to do this is to give your character a special skill or talent that sets him apart from other people. This might be something &#8230; <a href="http://writershelpingwriters.net/2015/01/talents-skills-thesaurus-entry-haggling/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a></p>
