<p>We&#8217;re so glad to be able to offer you something free to offset your generosity over the years. Because of your generosity, Becca &amp; I choose a charity to donate to on behalf of Writers Helping Writers.<strong> This year, we are giving $1000 to The Polaris Project.</strong> We can do this because you guys support us by buying books, so thank you! This worthy charity helps victims of human trafficking, and we couldn&#8217;t be happier to list it as our WHW 2014 Charity of the Year. To find out more about what they do, <a href="http://www.polarisproject.org/">please click HERE</a>.</p>
